tbamud-rwb build notes: Watcom C (obsolete)
=============================================

This file existed in stock TbaMUD to describe compiling the C server with Watcom C.
The Rust rewrite builds only with Cargo and targets modern Rust toolchains, so
Watcom C is not supported.  Build on a current operating system with:

    cargo build --release

See ../README.md and doc/porting.txt.
